replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"73fde7063b3cb4fe496c736ffbf4c6170b23ccf8","tid":1739581,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEiwqcy_a5U&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=50b629c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEiwqcy_a5U</a><br />\n<br />\n成班淨係識勇，2019年仲玩汽油彈，人地支槍唔知進化過幾多十代，唔好排隊去送頭啦好唔好?? 咁多手足冇人識整D真正有用又安全既野?"},{"pid":"373b4c20a685245f1d36c249165df63617636c14","tid":1739581,"uid":303141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"真普選真普選真普選"},{"pid":"afaae9ff12d14408fd0f6113eac1d6486eaf4a97","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d0bc44eef10dc7cae8893afa3cad40d1609a5cb2","tid":1739581,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d48712b503929eca2645cb055042cf7dc0b219c","tid":1739581,"uid":75879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:48:00.000Z","msg":"不要迷戀與狗博鬥 要做返多啲爭取民主大局上嘅事 如每星期一次嘅和理非遊行<br />\n不建議陣地 但兩軍對壘時 只有專雨才是救贖<br />\n前排搵嘢擋 越大件越好<br />\n後排不斷傅專上前 邊推進邊出專雨<br />\n一定要推進不要企定定 否則會變晒煙燻魚<br />\n專不要太大件 會影響射程<br />\n大量專雨落地後 會化成專陣 可阻水車銳武前進<br />\n火魔射程太近及量少珍貴 只有狗衝個時用嚟做屏障 不要亂放<br />\n好人一生平安 認同請勿廣傳"},{"pid":"af83bb44d3b415f69e4834c0d370fdffc9d40e6b","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e45d402679d749b52096917a215616160e910272","tid":1739581,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"243d073da6d9dad983f717a1668a665034b45ae1","tid":1739581,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"鄭立講咗樣嘢好啱，對家已經係用打仗兩軍對戰嘅心態同我哋開波，佢哋亦冇咗所謂嘅交戰規則（ROE - Rule of Engagement）好耐，只要佢覺得係抗爭者就唔理對方有冇犯法，打完再拉。面對咁嘅策略兼兩邊嘅武力都接近封頂，難聽啲講我哋已經進入咗內戰/ 準內戰嘅狀態，要調整翻個 mindset  去應對。"},{"pid":"c0a47338287cb061662d422c62478c50fd4d375c","tid":1739581,"uid":320495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18a1605c68b941d48a0ff1f67451ee76e4f11f61","tid":1739581,"uid":202050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e2538afe6e42484a8965d6a33f17f2866a9296a0","tid":1739581,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"好文<br />\n<br />\n第二點真係無諗過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69269cb01a8ca53aad5de6a434ec36bad4e2cf29","tid":1739581,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed0205b0184ddc49f8e357283e3fa474bd723c38","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:06:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42e2db9d4177a8e91480e817471628479721502d","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:15:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5b921914ab2c8d69fa602ead6e6d55a683eefb1","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"19f3800056ce8e90a49409921c8c2f5b0066b810","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:28:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0baa0732884437b8793047b7127390efedf66a09","tid":1739581,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:30:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b145f0c9cf14b97719e4cae1fcbb1f1c2521e22e","tid":1739581,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":